<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l4"><expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / als dem <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hochg<ex>eporn</ex></expan> fürſt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> hertʒog <expan>B<ex>er</ex>nhart</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> prawnſſvveig ewr <expan>brüd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l5">ein veſʒlein mit ſchönem vverck <expan>aufgehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>laſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / haben vvir <expan>deſſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> mals des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l6"><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> hertʒog <expan>B<ex>er</ex>nhart</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> ſelber auch <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> die habe </ab>
